data.description: Welcome home to a bright, spacious 4 bed, 4 bath, 3-car garage with shopping minutes away as well as close to Peterson, Schriever, & Fort Carson. Main-level has laminate wood floor throughout the dining room, living area, kitchen, breakfast area, half-bath, laundry room & garage entrance. Upstairs has four bedrooms, 2 full baths and some Mountain Views. The basement level has a large open space, another half-bath & bedroom with unfinished closet. Easily finished with additional storage space available. The 3rd bay of the garage has framing previously used as a dog space connecting to the exterior dog run & storage shed. The back yard is landscaped with rose bushes, trees, & paving stones with more room to put your personal touch.
